&lt;h1&gt;Double Sliding Van Window for Sprinter Driver Side Sliding Door | VWD SL101-DS&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Two independently sliding panels. Integrated bug screen and thermal privacy shade. 17% solar privacy glass. Clean all-glass exterior look.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-znvot4isz1/images/stencil/960w/products/2193/3522/VWD-SL101-DS-DOUBLE-SLIDER-WINDOW-SPRIINTER-VAN-SPRINTER-VAN-SCEEN-SHADE-DUAL-SLIDING-1__99316.1752015724.jpg?c=1&quot; alt=&quot;VWD SL101-DS double sliding van window for Sprinter driver side sliding door&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; height=&quot;231&quot; /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Key Features&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dual sliding panels for maximum ventilation control&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Integrated bug screen for airflow without insects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Integrated thermal privacy shade for light control and comfort&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;17% solar privacy glass for privacy, glare reduction, and UV control&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improved latching for secure daily use&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Urethane-bonded install for an OEM-style, weather-sealed finish&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Usually ships in 5 days or less&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 1 year&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Fitment&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Vehicle: Mercedes-Benz Sprinter Van&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Model years: 2007&amp;ndash;2026&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wheelbase: 144&quot; or 170&quot;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Roof height: low roof or high roof&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Window position: driver side sliding door&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Note: may not be compatible with some flare extensions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Technical Specifications&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;table border=&quot;1&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;8&quot;&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;SKU&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;SL101-DS&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Window Type&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Double-Sliding Van Window&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Vehicle&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Mercedes-Benz Sprinter Van&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Model Years&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;2007&amp;ndash;2026&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Wheelbase&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;144&quot; or 170&quot;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Roof Height&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Low Roof or High Roof&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Window Position&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Driver Side Sliding Door&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Glass&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;17% Solar Privacy Glass&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Screen&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Integrated Bug Screen&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Shade&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Integrated Thermal Privacy Shade&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Installation&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Urethane-Bonded&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Country of Origin&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Made in China&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Warranty&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;1 Year&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Ships&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Usually ships in 5 days or less&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Measurements&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Overall Size: 1402mm x 777mm (55.20&quot; x 30.6&quot;) &lt;br /&gt;Viewable Glass: 920mm x 467mm (36.22&quot; x 18.39&quot;) &lt;br /&gt;Opening: Up to 390mm x 467mm (15.35&quot; x 18.39&quot;)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Installation&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Confirm measurements before cutting. Dry-fit first. Deburr and protect exposed metal edges. Clean and prime per your urethane system requirements. Set the window and support it during cure. Allow full cure time before driving.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Installation instructions: &lt;a href=&quot;https://vanwindowsdirect.com/window-installation-instructions/&quot;&gt;View Full Window Installation Instructions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Explore Related Categories&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://vanwindowsdirect.com/sliding-van-windows/&quot;&gt;Sliding Van Windows&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://vanwindowsdirect.com/awning-van-windows/&quot;&gt;Awning Van Windows&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
