<h1>Double Sliding Van Window for Sprinter Driver Side Sliding Door | VWD SL101-DS</h1>
<p>Two independently sliding panels. Integrated bug screen and thermal privacy shade. 17% solar privacy glass. Clean all-glass exterior look.</p>
<figure><img src="https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-znvot4isz1/images/stencil/960w/products/2193/3522/VWD-SL101-DS-DOUBLE-SLIDER-WINDOW-SPRIINTER-VAN-SPRINTER-VAN-SCEEN-SHADE-DUAL-SLIDING-1__99316.1752015724.jpg?c=1" alt="VWD SL101-DS double sliding van window for Sprinter driver side sliding door" width="400" height="231" /></figure>
<h2>Key Features</h2>
<ul>
<li>Dual sliding panels for maximum ventilation control</li>
<li>Integrated bug screen for airflow without insects</li>
<li>Integrated thermal privacy shade for light control and comfort</li>
<li>17% solar privacy glass for privacy, glare reduction, and UV control</li>
<li>Improved latching for secure daily use</li>
<li>Urethane-bonded install for an OEM-style, weather-sealed finish</li>
<li>Usually ships in 5 days or less</li>
<li>Warranty: 1 year</li>
</ul>
<h2>Fitment</h2>
<ul>
<li>Vehicle: Mercedes-Benz Sprinter Van</li>
<li>Model years: 2007&ndash;2026</li>
<li>Wheelbase: 144" or 170"</li>
<li>Roof height: low roof or high roof</li>
<li>Window position: driver side sliding door</li>
<li>Note: may not be compatible with some flare extensions</li>
</ul>
