<h2>Measurements</h2>
<p>Overall Size: 1402mm x 777mm (55.20" x 30.6") <br />Viewable Glass: 920mm x 467mm (36.22" x 18.39") <br />Opening: Up to 390mm x 467mm (15.35" x 18.39")</p>
<h2>Installation</h2>
<p>Confirm measurements before cutting. Dry-fit first. Deburr and protect exposed metal edges. Clean and prime per your urethane system requirements. Set the window and support it during cure. Allow full cure time before driving.</p>
<p>Installation instructions: <a href="https://vanwindowsdirect.com/window-installation-instructions/">View Full Window Installation Instructions</a></p>
