</ul>
<h2>FAQ</h2>
<h3>What van does SL101-DS fit?</h3>
<p>Mercedes-Benz Sprinter vans (2007&ndash;2026). Position: driver's side sliding door. Fits 144 and 170 wheelbases. Low roof or high roof.</p>
<h3>What are the measurements?</h3>
<p>Overall size: 1402mm x 777mm (55.20" x 30.6"). Viewable glass: 920mm x 467mm (36.22" x 18.39"). Opening: up to 390mm x 467mm (15.35" x 18.39").</p>
<h3>What makes this different from a standard slider?</h3>
<p>SL101-DS has two independently sliding panels, so you can open the front, the rear, or both for better airflow control.</p>
<h3>Does it include a screen and shade?</h3>
<p>Yes. SL101-DS includes an integrated bug screen and an integrated thermal privacy shade.</p>
<h3>How is it installed?</h3>
<p>Urethane-bonded installation. Dry-fit first, prep and protect cut edges, clean and prime per urethane requirements, set the window, then support it during cure time.</p>
